Heat oven to 350 degrees F. Spray 1 1/2 quart casserole dish* with nonstick cooking spray. Stir Simply Potatoes(R) and salt in casserole dish until well blended. In medium bowl stir together all remaining ingredients. Spread topping evenly over Simply Potatoes(R). Bake, uncovered, 25 to 30 minutes or until topping is light golden brown and potatoes are heated through.